        {
            "title": "華爾街期貨在創紀錄收盤後小幅上漲;伊朗霍爾木茲提案成焦點",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/cnuI5Tv_0wsbw9g616LjUQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/asian_3_M_1440047966.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 華爾街期貨週一晚間小幅走高,此前基準指數創下新的紀錄收盤,美國總統唐納德·川普討論了伊朗重新開放<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"霍爾木茲海峽\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:霍爾木茲海峽;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/霍爾木茲海峽\">霍爾木茲海峽</a>的新提案。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至美國東部時間20:10(格林威治標準時間00:10),標普500指數期貨上漲0.2%至7,217.0點,納斯達克100指數期貨也上漲0.2%至27,487.75點。道指期貨上漲0.1%至49,397.0點。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>川普討論伊朗霍爾木茲海峽提案</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在週一的常規交易時段,標普500指數上漲0.1%創紀錄收盤,納斯達克綜合指數上漲0.2%創歷史新高,受科技股持續強勁表現支撐。道瓊工業平均指數下跌約0.1%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-ed498cf2-e2fd-3428-ae50-92cd6209af84-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據白宮消息,美國總統唐納德·川普討論了伊朗旨在緩解當前衝突的新提案,市場因此保持謹慎樂觀情緒。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該提案包括重新開放霍爾木茲海峽等措施,霍爾木茲海峽是全球石油運輸的關鍵通道,同時推遲更具爭議性的核談判。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">油價仍維持在數週高位附近,加劇了通脹擔憂,限制了更廣泛的風險偏好。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">能源成本上升一直是近期股市的主要壓力,特別是在通過霍爾木茲海峽的油輪運輸仍受限的情況下。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管存在地緣政治風險,但科技股的強勁勢頭以及對人工智能驅動增長的樂觀情緒為股市提供了支撐。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>本週大型科技股財報即將公布</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">投資者的焦點現在牢牢集中在本週密集的財報日程上,包括微軟(NASDAQ:MSFT)、蘋果(NASDAQ:AAPL)、亞馬遜(NASDAQ:AMZN)、Alphabet(NASDAQ:GOOGL)和Meta Platforms(NASDAQ:META)等主要科技公司將公布業績。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">超過三分之一的標普500成分股公司將在本週公布財報,分析師預期將迎來又一個季度的穩健利潤增長。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">週二開盤前,聯合包裹服務(NYSE:UPS)、通用汽車(NYSE:GM)、可口可樂(NYSE:KO)和捷藍航空(NASDAQ:JBLU)等公司將公布業績。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與此同時,市場正在為聯準會的政策會議做準備,利率普遍預期將維持不變,但主席傑羅姆·鮑威爾的評論可能會為未來政策路徑提供線索。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8F%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%A1%97%E6%9C%9F%E8%B2%A8%E5%9C%A8%E5%89%B5%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84%E6%94%B6%E7%9B%A4%E5%BE%8C%E5%B0%8F%E5%B9%85%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%B2-%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E9%9C%8D%E7%88%BE%E6%9C%A8%E8%8C%B2%E6%8F%90%E6%A1%88%E6%88%90%E7%84%A6%E9%BB%9E-011821056.html",
