        {
            "title": "美伊考慮重開荷莫茲海峽協議,油價走勢樂觀",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FSohemaPO_oD8FNraAnbyA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/indicatornews_6_M_1440048362.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 油價在週二亞洲早盤交易中上漲,延續近期漲勢,市場正密切關注美國與伊朗能否達成協議重新開放<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"荷莫茲海峽\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:荷莫茲海峽;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/荷莫茲海峽\">荷莫茲海峽</a>。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國WTI原油期貨上漲0.3%至96.62美元/桶,截至美國東部時間19:42(格林威治標準時間23:42),此前在上一交易日已飆升逾2%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本週稍早的報導顯示,德黑蘭提出了一項重新開放荷莫茲海峽並結束戰爭的新提案,華盛頓目前正在考慮該提案。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">但週一晚間《華爾街日報》的一篇報導顯示,美國總統唐納德·川普及其團隊對這項提議持懷疑態度,因為該提案建議推遲有關伊朗核活動的談判。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-2b3bc729-ae99-3a34-93b2-0f30e7cab4e5-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">終止伊朗的鈾濃縮活動並防止其發展核武器,是華盛頓在這場持續衝突中的兩大主要目標。《華爾街日報》報導稱,在考慮伊朗的新提案時,推遲核談判是川普的主要癥結點。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">但儘管伊朗提出了新提案,荷莫茲海峽仍基本處於關閉狀態,而美國也維持對伊朗的海上封鎖。通過荷莫茲海峽的石油流量仍然稀少,這使得原油價格獲得支撐,市場擔憂供應趨緊。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由巴基斯坦斡旋的美伊進一步會談計劃也在週末基本告吹,未來談判的狀況完全不確定。這一情況推動油價在週一大幅上漲,布蘭特原油重新逼近每桶110美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">除了伊朗戰爭之外,本週的焦點還集中在日本和美國的關鍵央行會議上,油價上漲可能會引發對未來數月能源驅動型通脹的警告。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E4%BC%8A%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E9%87%8D%E9%96%8B%E8%8D%B7%E8%8E%AB%E8%8C%B2%E6%B5%B7%E5%B3%BD%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0-%E6%B2%B9%E5%83%B9%E8%B5%B0%E5%8B%A2%E6%A8%82%E8%A7%80-010437109.html",
